"Pahaya pabbajissami, ","ja539:74.6":"tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:75.1":"Kadaham rajaputte ca, ","ja539:75.2":"sabbalankarabhusite; ","ja539:75.3":"Citravammadhare sure, ","ja539:75.4":"kancanaveladharine; ","ja539:75.5":"Pahaya pabbajissami, ","ja539:75.6":"tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:76.1":"Kadaham ariyagane ca, ","ja539:76.2":"vatavante alankate; ","ja539:76.3":"Haricandanalittange, ","ja539:76.4":"kasikuttamadharine; ","ja539:76.5":"Pahaya pabbajissami, ","ja539:76.6":"tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:77.1":"Kadaham amaccagane ca, ","ja539:77.2":"sabbalankarabhusite; ","ja539:77.3":"Pitavammadhare sure, ","ja539:77.4":"purato gacchamaline; ","ja539:77.5":"Pahaya pabbajissami, ","ja539:77.6":"tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:78.1":"Kadaham sattasata bhariya, ","ja539:78.2":"Sabbalankarabhusita; ","ja539:78.3":"Pahaya pabbajissami, ","ja539:78.4":"Tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:79.1":"Kadaham sattasata bhariya, ","ja539:79.2":"Susanna tanumajjhima; ","ja539:79.3":"Pahaya pabbajissami, ","ja539:79.4":"Tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:80.1":"Kadaham sattasata bhariya, ","ja539:80.2":"Assava piyabhanini; ","ja539:80.3":"Pahaya pabbajissami, ","ja539:80.4":"Tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:81.1":"Kadaham satapalam kamsam, ","ja539:81.2":"sovannam satarajikam; ","ja539:81.3":"Pahaya pabbajissami, ","ja539:81.4":"tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:82.1":"Kadassu mam hatthigumba, ","ja539:82.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","ja539:82.3":"Suvannakaccha matanga, ","ja539:82.4":"hemakappanavasasa. ","ja539:83.1":"Arulha gamaniyehi, ","ja539:83.2":"tomarankusapanibhi; ","ja539:83.3":"Yantam mam nanuyissanti, ","ja539:83.4":"tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:84.1":"Kadassu mam assagumba, ","ja539:84.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","ja539:84.3":"Ajaniyava jatiya, ","ja539:84.4":"sindhava sighavahana. ","ja539:85.1":"Arulha gamaniyehi, ","ja539:85.2":"illiyacapadharibhi; ","ja539:85.3":"Yantam mam nanuyissanti, ","ja539:85.4":"tam kudassu bhavissati. ","ja539:86.1":"Kadassu mam r